title: Longfellow 1 bedroom available in quiet neighborhood
posting_body: ['Longfellow Minneapolis apartment for rent.', 'Looking for a peaceful, quite abode?', 'Look no further!', 'This smaller, well-located building is where you need to be!', 'Units are a cozy mix of carpet and hardwood floors.', 'You won’t be far from a light-rail station as well as multiple bus lines.', 'Clustered around the light rail line are restaurants and shops for you to frequent.', 'Longfellow Minneapolis Apartment Amenities', 'Heat paid by management', 'Residents pay for electric, water and trash', 'High-speed USI fiber internet available', 'On major bus lines', 'Near Light Rail Station', 'Storage in building', 'Wall-unit ACs', 'Laundry on-site', 'Off-street parking', 'Small dogs welcome with additional deposit', 'Cats welcome with additional deposit', 'Attached photos are only an example of the apartments at this property, might not be actual unit available.', 'Prospect tenant agrees that has viewed and inspected the apartment before applying.', '1BR AVAILABLE September', 'Rent: $895 plus water, trash and electricity', "Deposit: Generally equal to one month's rent", 'App Fee: $40 (per person)', 'Please view our rental requirements here: <URL>', 'To see this apartment, please contact Jeff', 'show contact info', '.', 'To view our other properties, please visit: <URL>/', 'Attached photos are an example of the apartments at this property.', '3628 Minnehaha Avenue South, Minneapolis MN 55406']
